      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait so if it is pus is that bad? i don't really want to go back to the surgeon if i don't have to, it's a hassle. if i just do the warm compress and the ointment every few hours like you said, it'll definitely clear up on its own right? i'm pretty sure neosporin is strong enough to handle it.",
